3. cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) - The paper deals with multiuser detection, which is a problem in social and information networks. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper proposes a detection method based on MAP estimation and SOAV optimization, which are techniques commonly used in machine learning. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with signal processing and detection, which are topics related to multimedia.
